# Cloudflare Pages routing.
#
# /a2a/* is proxied to the demo-a2a Worker by the Pages Function at
# functions/a2a/[[path]].ts (which reads env.DEMO_A2A_URL — set by
# scripts/deploy-cloudflare.ts via `wrangler pages secret put`).
#
# Pages `_redirects` with status 200 to an external origin is silently
# ignored — that's why the proxy lives in a Function instead of here.
#
# This file is intentionally rule-free; kept as a marker that routing
# has been considered, and as a place for future SPA-fallback or
# host-internal redirects.
